# Project Walkthrough: MTDB Website Generation

## Changes Made
Successfully generated a complete, production-ready HTML/CSS website for the **Malaysian Talent Development Board (MTDB)** from scratch. The code adheres flawlessly to the "Euro-US / ThemeForest Enterprise" protocols defined in [antigravity_agent_config_summary.txt](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/antigravity_agent_config_summary.txt).

### 1. Structural Delivery
The following file structure has been fully populated and linked:
```text
mtdb-website/
├── css/
│   └── global.css          (The 5-Tier background system & Typography)
├── js/
│   └── main.js             (Sticky header & Swiper.js mechanics)
├── images/
│   ├── hero-1.jpg          (AI Generated)
│   ├── hero-2.jpg          (AI Generated)
│   ├── about-home.jpg      (AI Generated)
│   ├── about-banner.jpg    (AI Generated)
│   ├── services-banner.jpg (AI Generated)
│   └── aii-banner.jpg      (AI Generated)
├── index.html              (Dynamic hero, Trust Ribbon, 4-Column Grid)
├── about.html              (10-Year Roadmap, Vision, Mission)
├── services.html           (Service Range & 5-Step Delivery Flow)
├── faq.html                (MANDATORY: Bootstrap Accordion Q&A)
├── privacy.html            (MANDATORY: Mobile-readable Policy)
├── terms.html              (MANDATORY: Mobile-readable ToS)
└── project-details.html    (MANDATORY: Academy in Industry details template)
```

### 2. Design Implementation
- **5-Tier Backgrounds**: Evaluated and implemented `bg-layer-1` through `bg-layer-4` ensuring no flat, monotonous sections.
- **Micro-interactions**: The Global Header transitions to a fixed `.header-sticky` post 100px scroll.
- **Trust Ribbons**: Integrated right below the hero banner to instantly validate the 5.5% brain drain solution and RM27k net fiscal benefit per returning expert based on the user's provided PDF context.
- **Conversion Mechanisms**: Added the globally required `.float-wa` WhatsApp button floating CTA across all pages.

