## Validation Results
- **PDF Content Accuracy**: successfully parsed the `Malaysian Talent Development Board_PPT_V1 1.pdf` data and accurately distributed the 10-year roadmap, Mission Pillars, and Focus Industries into [about.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/mtdb-website/about.html), [index.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/mtdb-website/index.html), and [services.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/mtdb-website/services.html).
- **Global Configuration Met**: Mandatory execution of `project-details`, `faq`, `terms`, and `privacy` exist and are accessible from the global footer.

The website is fully built locally at [c:\Users\user\Desktop\antigravity\mtdb-website\index.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/mtdb-website/index.html). You can open this file in your browser right now to perform your visual review.
